reviewText: This is perhaps the worse music video I've ever seen. It was a Newport Jazz Festival from 1962, I believe, but the sound and video were terrible. Don't know if this was taken with a home video recorder, but whoever did it, did not improve on the quality at all. I've seen youtube videos of even earlier programs, and none of them looked this bad. I guess you get what you pay for. The price was low, but the quality was even lower.
My wife and I have all the Gypsy Caravan videos and we have been immensely satisfied with every single one!  You can never go wrong with Paulette and her people!
